description:
Body of an email to be sent to users. Please do not modify the text in curly braces "{example}", and please do not rearrange the order of the {braces} unless the translation requires it.

Note that some series of tags like "{boldStart}{code}{boldEnd}" or "{linkTagWithAuthenticatorHelpLinkStart}set up 2-Step Verification by Authenticator App{linkTagEnd}" are bundled together and should not be broken apart.
english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldStart}{code}{boldEnd} is your Roblox One-Time Code. Enter it into the login screen to log in. This code will expire in 15 minutes.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Do {boldStart}not{boldEnd} share this code. We will {boldStart}never{boldEnd} contact you to ask for it. If you did not request this code, there is no further action you need to take. If you receive numerous codes you did not request, we strongly encourage you to link a different email to your account(s) and {linkTagWithAuthenticatorHelpLinkStart}set up 2-Step Verification by Authenticator App{linkTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This login request was received from {geolocation}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank You,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}The Roblox Team
translation: Hai,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldStart}{code}{boldEnd}adalah Kode Sekali Pakai Roblox kamu. Masukkan kode tersebut ke layar log in untuk log in. Kode ini akan kedaluwarsa dalam 15 menit.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldStart}Jangan{boldEnd} bagikan kode ini. Kami {boldStart}tidak akan pernah{boldEnd} menghubungi kamu untuk meminta kode. Jika kamu tidak meminta kode ini, tidak ada tindakan lebih lanjut yang perlu kamu lakukan. Jika kamu menerima banyak kode yang tidak kamu minta, kami sangat sarankan kamu untuk menautkan email yang berbeda ke akun kamu dan {linkTagWithAuthenticatorHelpLinkStart}atur Verifikasi Dua Langkah dengan aplikasi Authenticator{linkTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Permintaan log in ini diterima dari {geolocation}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Terima kasih,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Tim Roblox

english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}{code}{emphasisEnd} is your Roblox 2-Step Verification code for {emphasisStart}{accountName}{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Enter the above code into the 2-Step Verification screen to finish logging in. This code will expire in 15 minutes.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}This login request was received from {emphasisStart}{geoLocationInformation}{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}IMPORTANT: Don't share your security codes with anyone. Roblox will never ask you for your codes. This can include things like texting your code, screensharing, etc. By sharing your security codes with someone else, you are putting your account and its content at high risk.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}Thank You,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Hai,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}{code}{emphasisEnd} adalah kode Verifikasi Dua Langkah untuk {emphasisStart}{accountName}{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Masukkan kode tersebut ke layar Verifikasi Dua Langkah untuk log in. Kode akan kedaluwarsa dalam 15 menit.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Permintaan log in diterima dari {emphasisStart}{geoLocationInformation}{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}PENTING: Jangan bagikan kode keamanan dengan siapa pun dan cara apa pun, seperti mengirim kode melalui SMS, membagikan layar perangkat kamu, dll. Roblox tidak akan pernah meminta kode kamu. Dengan membagikan kode keamanan dengan orang lain, akun kamu dan kontennya akan berisiko tinggi.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}Terima Kasih,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}Tim Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description: Footer of the two step verification login email.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there was a Roblox login attempt from a new browser or device. If you did not make this request, you are strongly advised to change your password.
translation: Jangan membalas email ini. Kamu menerima email ini karena ada upaya untuk log in ke akun Roblox kamu dari browser atau perangkat baru. Jika kamu tidak mengirim permintaan ini, kami sangat sarankan kamu untuk mengubah kata sandi.

description: Links displayed at the bottom of the two step verification login email. These go to: http://www.roblox.com/info/2sv, http://www.roblox.com/info/account-safety, http://www.roblox.com/info/help

Body for 2SV with Authenticator activation email for over 13 users
english: Hi {accountName},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}You have activated 2-Step Verification with Authenticator for your Roblox account. For some actions like logging in, you will need to enter a 6-digit security code from the Authenticator App.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Remember to save your backup codes in case you don't have access to the Authenticator app.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}IMPORTANT: Don't share your security codes with anyone. Roblox will never ask you for your codes. This can include things like texting your code, screensharing, etc. By sharing your security codes with someone else, you are putting your account and its content at high risk.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox
translation: Hai,{accountName},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Kamu telah mengaktifkan Verifikasi Dua Langkah dengan Authenticator untuk akun Roblox kamu. Untuk beberapa tindakan seperti log in, kamu akan diminta untuk memasukkan kode keamanan 6 digit dari aplikasi Authenticator.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Jangan lupa untuk menyimpan kode pemulihan. Jika nanti kamu tidak memiliki akses ke aplikasi Authenticator, kamu dapat menggunakan kode pemulihan tersebut.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}PENTING: Jangan bagikan kode keamanan dengan siapa pun dan cara apa pun, seperti mengirim kode melalui SMS, membagikan layar perangkat kamu, dll. Roblox tidak akan pernah meminta kode kamu. Dengan membagikan kode keamanan dengan orang lain, akun kamu dan kontennya akan berisiko tinggi.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Tim Roblox

english: Hello {accountName},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This message is to notify you that our support team has deactivated 2-Step Verification with Authenticator for your Roblox account. This typically occurs due to a support ticket you submitted or as a security measure to ensure the safety of your account. Hal ini biasanya terjadi karena email bantuan yang kamu kirim kepada kami atau tindakan keamanan untuk memastikan keamanan akun kamu. Kode keamanan dari aplikasi Authenticator tidak akan lagi diperlukan untuk beberapa tindakan seperti log in. We noticed that the password changed for your Roblox account: {userName}. If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, please click this link to undo the action:
{urlShown}

english:
Dear {userName},

We noticed you have changed the password for your account. If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, then we need you to contact customer service (https://www.roblox.com/support) to change the password back. That way we will know for sure that your account is secure and safe.

If you are happy with your new password on Roblox, you don't have to do anything! It's already set up.

Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please see the Roblox help page (https://www.roblox.com/help).

english: {paragraphStart}Your child is requesting to create the account {emphasisStart}{userName}{emphasisEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent's email address to create an account. In order for your child to complete the account creation process, you must consent to your child’s use of Roblox. You must enter the code below to complete the sign up flow and consent to your child’s use of Roblox. By entering the code, you and your child agree to the Roblox {aTagStartWithHref}{termsLink}{hrefEnd}Terms{aTagEnd}, including arbitration, and (b) You will supervise and be solely responsible for your child’s use of Roblox.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Verification Code: {code}{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Parent's Guide To Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}We recommend that you visit our {aTagStartWithHref}{parentsLink}{hrefEnd}Parent’s Guide{aTagEnd} to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privacy{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You may remove your child's account anytime by contacting customer service at {aTagStartWithHref}{supportLink}{hrefEnd}https://www.roblox.com/support{aTagEnd}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPolicyLink}{hrefEnd}Privacy Policy{aTagEnd} for more information.{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Anak Anda ingin membuat akun {emphasisStart}{userName}{emphasisEnd} di Roblox, platform pengalaman virtual online bagi anak-anak untuk berimajinasi, berkreasi, dan bermain bersama di dunia 3D imersif yang dikembangkan oleh pengguna.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Anak Anda telah memberikan kami nama pengguna, tanggal lahir, dan alamat email orang tua untuk membuat akun. Agar anak Anda dapat menyelesaikan proses pembuatan akun, Anda harus menyetujui penggunaan Roblox oleh anak Anda. Untuk menyelesaikan proses pendaftaran dan menyetujui penggunaan Roblox oleh anak Anda, masukkan kode di bawah ini. Dengan memasukkan kode, Anda dan anak Anda menyetujui {aTagStartWithHref}{termsLink}{hrefEnd}Ketentuan{aTagEnd} Roblox, termasuk arbitrase, dan (b) Anda akan memonitor dan sepenuhnya bertanggung jawab atas penggunaan Roblox anak Anda.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Kode Verifikasi: {code}{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Panduan Orang Tua{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Kami merekomendasikan Anda untuk mengunjungi {aTagStartWithHref}{parentsLink}{hrefEnd}Panduan Orang Tua{aTagEnd} untuk membantu Anda mengenal platform kami dan menemukan tip bermanfaat untuk menciptakan pengalaman yang positif bagi anak Anda di Roblox.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privasi{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Anda dapat menghapus akun anak Anda kapan saja dengan menghubungi dukungan pelanggan di {aTagStartWithHref}{supportLink}{hrefEnd}https://www.roblox.com/support{aTagEnd}. Email Anda tidak akan digunakan untuk tujuan lain, dibagikan ke pihak ketiga, atau digabungkan dengan informasi pribadi lainnya yang didapatkan dari anak Anda. Silakan baca {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPolicyLink}{hrefEnd}Kebijakan Privasi{aTagEnd} kami untuk informasi lebih lanjut.{paragraphEnd}

description: Email body of verification email that is sent out when an under 13 user adds an email to the account
english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Your child created the account {boldTagStart}{username}{boldTagEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds. Our platform also provides a free development tool called “Roblox Studio” that allows users to create anything they imagine, from simple drag-and-drop building experiences to complex multiplayer games. Millions of kids have used Roblox to imagine what it’s like to create the ultimate theme park, compete as a professional race car driver, star in a fashion show, or simply build a dream home and hang out with friends.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This email is to inform you that your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent’s email address. The parent’s email address is only used for account management, password resets if the child forgets their password, and to notify parents of changes to the child’s account access. To verify your email address, please click the button below: {lineBreak}{lineBreak}{aTagStartWithHref}{verificationLink}{hrefEnd}{buttonStart}Verify Email{buttonEnd}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldTagStart}About Roblox{boldTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox is dedicated to building an enjoyable, family-friendly environment. We are constantly evolving our safety features and working with digital safety experts to ensure that all players have a safe, comfortable place to play, chat, and collaborate on creative projects. We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: {aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox also offers {boldTagStart}parental controls{boldTagEnd}. Parents can enable a parent PIN and change their child’s communication and chat settings. You can find these controls by visiting the security and privacy tabs in the account settings while logged into your child’s account.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}To add a parent PIN, please visit: {aTagStartWithHref}{accountSecurityLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSecurityLink}{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}To change chat settings, please visit: {aTagStartWithHref}{accountPrivacyLink}{hrefEnd}{accountPrivacyLink}{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldTagStart}Privacy{boldTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}You may remove your child's account by contacting customer service at {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our privacy policy for more information at {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}The Roblox Team {lineBreak}{lineBreak} Do not reply to this email directly. {lineBreak}{lineBreak} {aTagStartWithHref}{robloxWebsiteLink}{hrefEnd}{robloxWebsiteLink}{aTagEnd} {lineBreak}{lineBreak} {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}
translation: Hai,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Anak Anda telah membuat akun {boldTagStart}{username}{boldTagEnd} di Roblox, platform pengalaman virtual online bagi anak-anak untuk berimajinasi, berkreasi, dan bermain bersama di dunia 3D yang imersif. Platform kami juga menyediakan Roblox Studio, yaitu alat gratis bagi pengguna untuk membuat apa pun yang mereka bayangkan, dari pengalaman virtual membangun seret-lepas yang sederhana hingga game multipemain yang rumit. Jutaan anak telah menggunakan Roblox untuk membayangkan seperti apa kalau mereka membuat theme park yang keren, berkompetisi sebagai pengendara mobil balap profesional, menjadi model fashion show, atau membuat rumah impian, dan hang out dengan teman mereka.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Email ini untuk menginformasikan bahwa anak Anda telah memberikan nama pengguna, tanggal lahir, dan alamat email orang tua kepada kami. Alamat orang tua hanya akan digunakan untuk mengelola akun, mereset kata sandi jika anak mereka lupa kata sandi, dan untuk memberikan notifikasi kepada orang tua akan perubahan akses akun anak mereka. Untuk memverifikasi alamat email Anda, silakan klik tombol di bawah: {lineBreak}{lineBreak}{aTagStartWithHref}{verificationLink}{hrefEnd}{buttonStart}Verifikasi Email{buttonEnd}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldTagStart}Tentang Roblox{boldTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox berdedikasi untuk membangun lingkungan yang ramah keluarga dan menyenangkan. Kami senantiasa mengembangkan fitur keamanan dan bekerja dengan pakar keamanan siber untuk memastikan bahwa semua pemain memiliki tempat yang aman dan nyaman untuk bermain, chat, dan berkolaborasi di proyek yang kreatif. description: Email body of verification email that is sent out when an under 13 user adds an email to the account
english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Your child created the account {username} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and explore together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds. Our platform also provides a free development tool called “Roblox Studio” that allows users to create anything they imagine, from simple drag-and-drop building experiences to complex multiplayer games. Millions of kids have used Roblox to imagine what it’s like to create the ultimate theme park, compete as a professional race car driver, star in a fashion show, or simply build a dream home and hang out with friends.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This email is to inform you that your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent’s email address. The parent’s email address is only used for account management, password resets if the child forgets their password, and to notify parents of changes to the child’s account access. To verify your email address, please click the button below:{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{verificationLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}About Roblox{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox is dedicated to building an enjoyable, family-friendly environment. We are constantly evolving our safety features and working with digital safety experts to ensure that all users have a safe, comfortable place to explore, chat, and collaborate on creative projects. We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: {parentalPageLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox also offers parental controls. Parents can enable a parent PIN and change their child’s communication and chat settings. You can find these controls by visiting the security and privacy tabs in the account settings while logged into your child’s account.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}To add a parent PIN, please visit: {accountSecurityLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}To change chat settings, please visit: {chatPrivacyLink} {lineBreak}{lineBreak}Privacy{lineBreak}{lineBreak} You may remove your child's account by contacting customer service at {supportPageLink}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our privacy policy for more information at {privacyPageLink}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}The Roblox Team{lineBreak}Do not reply to this email directly.{lineBreak}{robloxWebiteLink}{lineBreak}{supportPageLink}
translation: Hai,{lineBreak} {lineBreak}Anak Anda telah membuat akun {username} di Roblox, platform pengalaman virtual online bagi anak-anak untuk berimajinasi, berkreasi, dan bermain bersama di dunia 3D yang imersif. Platform kami juga menyediakan Roblox Studio, yaitu alat gratis bagi pengguna untuk membuat apa pun yang mereka bayangkan, dari pengalaman virtual membangun seret-lepas yang sederhana hingga game multipemain yang rumit. Jutaan anak telah menggunakan Roblox untuk membayangkan seperti apa kalau mereka membuat theme park yang keren, berkompetisi sebagai pengendara mobil balap profesional, menjadi model fashion show, atau membuat rumah impian, dan hang out dengan teman mereka.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Email ini untuk menginformasikan bahwa anak Anda telah memberikan nama pengguna, tanggal lahir, dan alamat email orang tua kepada kami. Alamat orang tua hanya akan digunakan untuk mengelola akun, mereset kata sandi jika anak mereka lupa kata sandi, dan untuk memberikan notifikasi kepada orang tua akan perubahan akses akun anak mereka. Orang tua dapat mengaktifkan PIN orang tua dan mengubah pengaturan komunikasi dan chat. Anda dapat menemukan kendali ini dengan mengunjungi tab keamanan dan privasi di pengaturan akun saat log in ke akun anak Anda.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Untuk menambahkan PIN orang tua, kunjungi:{accountSecurityLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Untuk mengubah pengaturan chat, kunjungi{chatPrivacyLink} {lineBreak}{lineBreak}Privasi{lineBreak}{lineBreak} Anda dapat menghapus akun anak Anda kapan saja dengan menghubungi dukungan pelanggan di {supportPageLink}. english: Dear Roblox user,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}We noticed that you have changed the email address for your {username} account from {oldEmailAddress} to {newEmailAddress}. You will also need to enter a new password. Agar akunmu tetap aman, kamu akan diminta untuk mengatur kata sandi baru.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Jangan membalas email ini. Jika kamu memiliki pertanyaan, kunjungi Pusat Bantuan Roblox.

english: Dear {username},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}We noticed that you have changed your email address from {oldEmailAddress} to {newEmailAddress}. If you made this change, feel free to disregard this email.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}If you did not make this change, or did so by mistake, please click this link to change the email back: {revertAccountEmailLink}. To keep your account safe, you will be asked to set a new password.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please visit our Help Center ({accountHelpLink}).
translation: Hai {username},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Alamat email kamu telah diubah dari {oldEmailAddress} menjadi {newEmailAddress}. Jika kamu melakukan perubahan ini, abaikan email ini.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Akan tetapi, jika kamu tidak melakukannya atau melakukannya secara tidak sengaja, klik tautan yang berikut untuk mengubah kembali alamat email: {revertAccountEmailLink}. Agar akunmu tetap aman, kamu akan diminta untuk mengatur kata sandi baru.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Jangan membalas email ini. Jika kamu memiliki pertanyaan, kunjungi Pusat Bantuan ({accountHelpLink}) Roblox.

description: DEPRECATED, DO NOT INCLUDE
english: Hello Roblox user, {lineBreaks}Your username change request has been processed. Your username was changed from {oldUsername} to {newUsername}. If you did not request a username change, seek account help from Roblox Support ({accountHelpLink}). Please do not reply to this email.
translation: Hai pengguna Roblox, {lineBreaks}Permintaan perubahan nama pengguna kamu sudah diproses. Nama pengguna kamu sudah diubah dari {oldUsername} menjadi {newUsername}. Jika kamu tidak mengirim permintaan perubahan ini, hubungi Bantuan Roblox ({accountHelpLink}). Jangan membalas email ini.

english: I am invited to a private server
This setting controls who can join this user in private servers - servers that can only be joined by invitation of the server owner.
translation: Pengaturan ini mengendalikan siapa yang dapat bergabung dengan pengguna ini di server privat - server yang hanya terbuka untuk undangan dari pemilik server.

english: Who can invite me to private servers?
translation: Siapa yang dapat mengundang saya ke server privat?

description: Subject for email verification email, which is used to let the user confirm that their email address is associated with this roblox account.
Body text for email verification email. This comes before a button that the user can click to proceed with confirming that they want to associate this email to the given Roblox account.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thanks for choosing to secure your Roblox account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} by providing an email address.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}If you submitted this request, please click the button below to complete the verification process:{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Hai,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Terima kasih telah {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}memberikan alamat email untuk mengamankan akun kamu. {paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Jika kamu mengirim permintaan ini, klik tombol di bawah untuk menyelesaikan proses verifikasi:{paragraphEnd}

description: Text on a button in the email verification email. Clicking this button lets the user confirm that they want this email address to be associated with their Roblox account for security purposes.
Second part of the body of the email verification email. This comes after the 'verify email' button.
Footer displayed at the bottom of the 'email verification' email.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there has been an attempt to verify a Roblox account with your email. If you did not make this request, please disregard this email.
translation: Jangan membalas ke email ini. Kamu menerima email ini karena telah ada upaya untuk memverifikasi akun Roblox dengan menggunakan email kamu. Jika kamu tidak melakukannya, abaikan email ini.

description: Informative links at the bottom of the 'email verification' email.
Subject line for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is sent to the parent of the user, who is responsible for taking action on authorizing the email.

First part of the body text for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is directed at the parent of the user. Below this text is an "I Agree, Verify Email" button that the parent can click to proceed.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child created the account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent's email address. Please confirm this email address is correct by {emphasisStart}clicking the button below to complete the validation process{emphasisEnd}. Regardless of whether you validate the parental email address or not, the child will still be able to retain their account and chat with others.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}By clicking the "I Agree, Validate Email" button you also agree that (a) You and your child agree to the Roblox {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Terms{aTagEnd}, including arbitration, and (b) You will supervise and be solely responsible for your child’s use of Roblox.{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Hai,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Anak Anda telah membuat akun{emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} di Roblox, platform game online bagi anak-anak untuk berimajinasi, berkreasi, dan bermain bersama di dunia 3D imersif yang dikembangkan oleh pengguna.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Anak Anda telah memberikan nama pengguna, tanggal lahir, dan alamat email orang tua kepada kami. Harap konfirmasikan bahwa ini adalah alamat email yang benar dengan {emphasisStart}mengklik tombol di bawah untuk menyelesaikan proses validasi{emphasisEnd}. Terlepas dari apakah Anda memvalidasi email orang tua atau tidak, anak Anda tetap dapat mempertahankan akunnya dan chat dengan pengguna lain.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Dengan mengklik tombol "Saya Setuju, Validasi Email", Anda juga menyetujui bahwa (a) Anda dan anak Anda menyetujui {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Ketentuan{aTagEnd} Roblox, termasuk arbitrasi dan (b) Anda akan memonitor dan sepenuhnya bertanggung jawab atas penggunaan Roblox anak Anda.{paragraphEnd}

description: Text of the button in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. The text of this button is referred to by name in the first part of the email body ('by clicking "I Agree, Validate Email"...'), so the name should be consistent.

Second part of the body text in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is shown after a button that the parent can click to proceed with email verification. 'Parent's Guide to Roblox' and 'Privacy' are paragraph headers.
english: {paragraphStart}You can set your child's safety and parental control settings for their Roblox account at {aTagStartWithHref}{accountSettingsLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSettingsLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Parent's Guide to Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: {aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privacy{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You may remove your child's account anytime by contacting customer service at {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our privacy policy for more information at {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thank You,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Anda dapat mengelola pengaturan kendali orang tua dan keamanan akun Roblox anak Anda di {aTagStartWithHref}{accountSettingsLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSettingsLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Panduan Orang Tua{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Kami merekomendasikan Anda untuk mengunjungi Panduan Orang Tua untuk membantu Anda mengenal platform kami dan menemukan tip bermanfaat untuk menciptakan pengalaman virtual yang positif bagi anak Anda di Roblox: {aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privasi{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Anda dapat menghapus akun anak Anda kapan saja dengan menghubungi bantuan di {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}. Email Anda tidak akan digunakan untuk tujuan lain, dibagikan ke pihak ketiga, atau digabungkan dengan informasi pribadi lainnya yang didapatkan dari anak Anda. Silakan baca kebijakan privasi kami untuk informasi lebih lanjut di {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Terima kasih,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}Tim Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description: Footer at the bottom of the 'email verification' email for users under 13.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there has been an attempt to verify a Roblox account with your email. If you did not make this request, please disregard this email.
translation: Jangan membalas ke email ini. Kamu menerima email ini karena telah ada upaya untuk memverifikasi akun Roblox dengan menggunakan email kamu. Jika kamu tidak melakukannya, abaikan email ini.

description: Links at the bottom of the 'email verification' email for users under 13.

english: When this setting is enabled, the PIN must be provided before changing settings.
translation: Saat pengaturan ini diaktifkan, masukkan PIN untuk dapat mengubah pengaturan.

english: When this setting is enabled, this account can only access content that is appropriate for all audiences. Additionally, Communication Settings (under the {linkStart}Privacy{linkEnd} page) will be set to Off.
translation: Saat pengaturan ini diaktifkan, akun ini hanya dapat mengakses konten yang sesuai untuk semua pengguna. Selain itu, Pengaturan Komunikasi (di bagian halaman {linkStart}Privasi{linkEnd}) akan dimatikan.

english: Parental Controls allow parents to choose the correct settings that will control what experiences their child can access.
translation: Dengan Kendali Orang Tua, orang tua dapat memilih pengaturan yang tepat yang akan mengendalikan pengalaman virtual apa yang dapat diakses oleh anak mereka.

english: This setting controls what type of experiences this user is allowed to visit.
translation: Pengaturan ini mengendalikan tipe pengalaman virtual yang dapat dikunjungi oleh pengguna ini.

english: Communication Settings are locked because Account Restrictions (under {linkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} page) are enabled
translation: Pengaturan Komunikasi terkunci karena Pembatasan Akun (di bagian halaman {linkStart}Kendali Orang Tua{linkEnd}) diaktifkan

description: DO NOT TRANSLATE, CAN BE DELETED
Label next to toggle for enabling email-based two step verification.
Label next to toggle for enabling authenticator-based two step verification.
Requirement for enabling authenticator-based two step verification.
Displayed as help text when authenticator-based two step verification is already enabled.
english: Download an app on your phone to generate unique security codes. Suggested apps include Google Authenticator, Microsoft Authenticator, and Twilio's Authy.
translation: Download aplikasi di ponsel kamu untuk membuat kode keamanan unik. Aplikasi yang disarankan seperti Google Authenticator, Microsoft Authenticator, dan Twilio Authy.

english: Scan the QR code above into your authenticator app, then enter the generated code below.
translation: Scan kode QR di atas ke aplikasi autentikasi kamu lalu masukkan kode di bawah.

english: Enter the manual entry key above into your authenticator app, then enter the generated code below.
translation: Masukkan kunci entri manual di atas ke aplikasi autentikasi kamu lalu masukkan kode di bawah.

description: Message to user for manual Authenticator code entry.
english: Can't scan the QR code? Click here for manual entry.
translation: Tidak dapat scan kode QR? Klik di sini untuk memasukkan kode secara manual.

english: QR code has expired. Please close the modal and try again.
translation: Kode QR sudah kedaluwarsa. Tutup jendela dan coba lagi.

description: The title of the dialog that asks you to input your password before generating recovery codes.
The title of the dialog displaying the newly generated recovery codes.
The description text on the dialog prompting the user to generate new recovery codes by providing their password.
english: Please enter your account password to generate new backup codes.
translation: Masukkan kata sandi akun kamu untuk membuat kode pemulihan.

english: These are your new backup codes. Please save them as you will not be able to see the codes again later.
translation: Ini adalah kode pemulihan baru kamu. Simpan kode ini karena kamu tidak akan dapat melihatnya lagi nanti.

description: Check box confirming the user has saved their recovery codes.
translation: Saya sudah menyimpan kode pemulihan saya

description: A label on the modal for generating new recovery codes  giving notice that the number of remaining unused recovery codes will no longer work.
english: {activeCodeCount} backup codes will become invalid when new ones are generated.
translation: {activeCodeCount} kode pemulihan akan menjadi tidak valid setelah kode yang baru dibuat.

description: Label next to button for generating two step verification recovery codes.
Help text on the two step verification recovery codes section card.
english: Generate and use backup codes in case you lose access to your 2-Step Verification option. Do not share your backup codes with anyone.
translation: Buat dan gunakan kode pemulihan kalau nanti kamu kehilangan akses ke opsi Verifikasi Dua Langkah. Jangan bagikan kode pemulihan dengan siapa pun.

english: You need {robuxIcon} {robuxToBuy} more to change your username. Would you like to buy more Robux?
translation: Kamu perlu lebih banyak {robuxIcon} {robuxToBuy} untuk mengubah nama penggunamu. Kamu ingin membeli lebih banyak Robux?

english: To keep you and the community safe, age verification is required to access certain features on Roblox.
translation: Agar kamu dan komunitas tetap aman, verifikasi usia diperlukan untuk mengakses fitur tertentu di Roblox.

description: Label next to toggle after enabling email-based two step verification.
english: Your Account is Protected via Email Verification
translation: Akun Kamu Dilindungi via Verifikasi Email

description: Label next to button for generating two step verification recovery codes after two step verification recovery codes have already been generated.
Message to user that appears after the user has generated recovery codes.
translation: Kamu memiliki {activeCodeCount} kode pemulihan yang belum digunakan.

description: Virtual transaction 2SV
english: 2-step Verification is required to make further transactions.
translation: Verifikasi Dua Langkah diperlukan untuk melakukan transaksi lebih lanjut.

english: If you change your birthday, your age will no longer be verified.
translation: Jika kamu mengubah tanggal lahir, usia kamu tidak akan lagi terverifikasi.

description: prompt to add screentime restrictions for children in parental controls
english: You can add restriction hours to your child's account.
translation: Anda dapat menerapkan batasan waktu di akun anak Anda.

description: prompt for selecting restriction hours time. ex. "Blocked From 6:00 AM"
prompt for selecting restriction hours time. ex. "Blocked Until 9:00 AM"
prompt for selecting restriction days. ex. "Repeat every Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday"

english: Your time zone has been updated successfully!
translation: Zona waktu kamu sudah berhasil di-update

description: button for adding screentime restrictions
error shown when user sets screentime restrictions that allow less than 1 hour of playtime
english: People must have at least one hour of allowed time.
translation: Waktu yang diizinkan harus minimal satu jam.

description: error shown if user inputs a screentime restriction with invalid times (ex 4pm to 10am)
english: Blocked Until time must be later than the Blocked From time.
translation: Waktu Diblokir Hingga harus setelah waktu Diblokir Dari.

description: prompts a user to update their time zone when stored time zone doesn't match current device timezone
english: Looks like you are in the time zone: {timeZone}, update time zone?
translation: Sepertinya kamu berada di zona waktu: {timeZone}. Update zona waktu?

description: prompts user to save screentime restriction settings
english: Click on Save to update your changes.

description: ex. Every Wednesday, Monday, Tuesday. Should include the space after "every" (if this is relevant in translated language)
heading for section where parents can add restrictions to when their children can play Roblox

english: You must select at least one day of the week.
translation: Kamu harus memilih setidaknya satu hari dalam seminggu.

description: tooltip text for korea screentime controls
english: The Youth Protection Revision Act, commonly known as the Shutdown Law or Cinderella Law, is an act of the South Korean National Assembly which forbids children under the age of 16 to play online video games between the hours of 00:00 and 06:00.
translation: Youth Protection Revision Act, yang umumnya dikenal sebagai Shutdown Law atau Cinderella Law, adalah hukum dari Majelis Nasional Korea Selatan yang melarang anak yang berusia di bawah 16 tahun untuk bermain game video online dari antara pukul 24.00 hingga 06.00.

description: tooltip label for korea screentime curfew law
english: 12am - 6am is automatically restricted and cannot be edited.
translation: 24.00 - 06.00 dibatasi secara otomatis dan tidak dapat diedit.

description: robux spend friction
english: Improve your account security. A code will be required for some actions like logging in.
translation: Tingkatkan keamanan akun kamu. Kode akan diperlukan untuk sebagian tindakan seperti log in.

english: Your username change request has been processed. Your username was changed from {oldUsername} to {newUsername}. If you did not request a username change, please review our account help information at our {startLink}Help Center{endLink}. Please do not reply to directly to this email as replies to this email address are not received.
translation: Permintaan perubahan nama pengguna kamu sudah diproses. Nama pengguna kamu sudah diubah dari {oldUsername} menjadi {newUsername}. Jika kamu tidak mengirim permintaan perubahan ini, harap baca informasi bantuan akun kami di {startLink}Dukungan Pelanggan{endLink} Jangan membalas email ini karena balasan ke email tidak akan diterima oleh kami.

description: Make sure that user wants to disable email two step verification when another two step verification method exists.
english: If you turn off 2-Step Verification with Email, a security code from your email will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. Are you sure?
translation: Jika kamu mematikan Verifikasi Dua Langkah dengan email, kode keamanan dari email kamu tidak akan lagi diperlukan untuk beberapa tindakan seperti log in. Kamu yakin?

description: Make sure that user wants to disable authenticator two step verification when another two step verification method exists.
english: If you turn off 2-Step Verification with Authenticator, a security code from the Authenticator App will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. Are you sure?
translation: Jika kamu mematikan Verifikasi Dua Langkah dengan aplikasi Authenticator, kode keamanan dari aplikasi Authenticator tidak akan lagi diperlukan untuk beberapa tindakan seperti log in. Kamu yakin?

english: You must be at least 18 years old to save screen time restrictions.
translation: Kamu harus berusia setidaknya 18 tahun untuk dapat mengatur batasan durasi layar.

english: Enabling voice chat will use your microphone input in voice enabled experiences.
translation: Mengaktifkan chat suara akan menggunakan mikrofon perangkat kamu di pengalaman virtual dengan suara yang diaktifkan.

english: By clicking 'Verify My Age' you will be completing an ID verification process operated by our third party service provider.
translation: Dengan mengklik "Verifikasi Usia Saya", kamu akan melakukan proses verifikasi identitas yang dilaksanakan oleh penyedia layanan pihak ketiga kami.

description:
Text of the button in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. The text of this button is referred to by name in the first part of the email body ('By clicking "I Agree, Validate Email"...'), so the name should be consistent with 
Description.VerificationEmail.Body.Under13.V3.
Appears on the Authenticator enabling modal.
translation: Klik di sini untuk informasi selengkapnya

english: Someone accepts my group join request
translation: Seseorang menerima permintaan bergabung ke grup saya

description: For a toggle to make the user appear offline for some time

english: Warning: You currently have both 2 Step Verification via Email and Authenticator app turned on. To keep your account super safe, we recommend that you have 2 Step Verification via Authenticator turned on, and 2 Step Verification via Email turned off.
translation: Peringatan: Saat ini Verifikasi Dua Langkah via email dan aplikasi Authenticator dinyalakan. Agar akun kamu tetap sangat aman, kami merekomendasikan kamu untuk menyalakan Verifikasi Dua Langkah via Authenticator dan mematikan Verifikasi Dua Langkah via email.

description: description of the visibility toggle
english: This feature allows you to appear offline to all users for 12 hours or until turned off.
translation: Fitur ini dapat membuat kamu tampak offline ke semua pengguna sampai dengan 12 jam atau hingga dimatikan.

description: Error message when resend code for verify phone is flooded.
english: Too many requests to resend code. Please try again later.
translation: Terlalu banyak permintaan untuk mengirim ulang kode. Coba lagi nanti.

description: Error message when resend code for verify phone is flooded.
english: Too many requests to resend code. Please try again later.
translation: Terlalu banyak permintaan untuk mengirim ulang kode. Coba lagi nanti.

english: This setting limits the amount of spend permitted on the under 13 year old user's account per calendar month. Default platform spending restrictions will apply when this setting is turned off.
translation: Pengaturan ini membatasi jumlah uang yang diizinkan untuk dipakai setiap bulannya bagi akun dengan pengguna yang berusia di bawah 13 tahun. Batasan pengeluaran default akan berlaku saat pengaturan ini dimatikan.

english: This setting controls notifications on spend sent to the verified parental email on the under 13 user's account. Parents who select the default will only receive email notifications when spend levels are exceedingly high in a given calendar month.
translation: Pengaturan ini mengendalikan notifikasi yang dikirim ke email orang tua tentang pengeluaran untuk akun dengan pengguna yang berusia di bawah 13 tahun. Orang tua yang memilih default hanya akan menerima notifkasi email jika level penggunaan sangat tinggi dalam satu bulan.

translation: Hai {username},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Alamat email kamu telah diubah dari {oldEmailAddress} menjadi {newEmailAddress}. Jika kamu melakukan perubahan ini, abaikan email ini.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Akan tetapi, jika kamu tidak melakukannya atau melakukannya secara tidak sengaja, klik tautan yang berikut untuk mengubah kembali alamat email: {revertAccountEmailLink}. Agar akun kamu tetap aman, kamu akan diminta untuk mengatur kata sandi baru.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Jangan membalas email ini. Jika kamu memiliki pertanyaan, kunjungi Pusat Bantuan Roblox.

translation: Batasan pengeluaran bulanan harus di bawah {maxMonthlySpendLimit} USD

description: Enable 2sv modal header.

english: To turn on 2-Step Verification, please verify account password.
translation: Untuk menyalakan Verifikasi Dua Langkah, verifikasikan kata sandi akun.

english: Verification is required to continue with your virtual transaction.
translation: Verifikasi Dua Langkah diperlukan untuk melanjutkan transaksi virtual kamu.

english: Verification is required to continue with your trade.
translation: Verifikasi Dua Langkah diperlukan untuk melanjutkan trade.

description: The message users get if we have turned off voice chat opt in.
english: Voice chat enrollment has been temporarily disabled.
translation: Pendaftaran chat suara telah dinonaktifkan untuk sementara.

description: filtering level for in app chat

english: All text chat is scanned for language that is inappropriate within the Roblox community. This setting controls what you can send and receive while chatting with others on Roblox.
translation: Semua chat teks di-scan jika ada kata yang tidak pantas bagi komunitas Roblox. Pengaturan ini mengendalikan apa yang dapat kamu kirim dan terima saat chat dengan pengguna lain di Roblox.

description: This text will replace the normal text next to the voice chat opt in toggle if they have been banned from voice chat. The date they will be banned until will be right after this text, which is why the sentence ends partway.
english: Due to the violation of our Community Standards, we have temporarily revoked your access to voice chat until
translation: Oleh karena pelanggaran terhadap Standar Komunitas, kami telah menangguhkan akses kamu ke chat suara hingga

description: This text will replace the normal description next to the voice chat opt-in toggle if the user has been MVP banned from voice chat.
english: Due to multiple violations of our Community Standards, we have temporarily revoked your access to voice chat until the Beta phase ends.
translation: Oleh karena beberapa pelanggaran terhadap Standar Komunitas, kami telah menangguhkan akses kamu ke chat suara hingga fase Beta berakhir.

description: Error message.
english: The Guilded profile url is invalid.

description: Message a user gets when they have been banned from voice chat.
english: Your access to voice chat has been suspended for violating our Community Standards.
translation: Oleh karena pelanggaran terhadap Standar Komunitas, kami telah menangguhkan akses kamu ke chat suara.

english: Verification is required to continue with your resale.
translation: Verifikasi Dua Langkah diperlukan untuk melanjutkan penjualan kembali.

description: Feedback to user when they've copied their manual authenticator key to clipboard.

english: Spend restrictions can't be disabled in your region.
translation: Batasan penggunaan tidak dapat dinonaktifkan di wilayah kamu.

english: Success! Monthly Spend Restrictions have been setted up.
translation: Batasan Penggunaan Uang Bulanan telah berhasil diatur.

english: Spend restrictions cannot be disabled in your region.
translation: Batasan penggunaan tidak dapat dinonaktifkan di wilayah kamu.

english: This setting limits the amount of spend permitted on the under {age} year old user's account per calendar month. Default platform spending restrictions will apply when this setting is turned off.
translation: Pengaturan ini membatasi jumlah uang yang diizinkan untuk dipakai setiap bulannya bagi akun dengan pengguna yang berusia di bawah {age} tahun. Batasan pengeluaran default akan berlaku saat pengaturan ini dimatikan.

description: Description that appears in the background when both email and authenticator 2sv are enabled
english: You currently have both 2-Step Verification via Email and Authenticator App turned on. In most cases, to keep your account secure, you will only be allowed to log in via Authenticator.
translation: Saat ini Verifikasi Dua Langkah via email dan aplikasi Authenticator dinyalakan. Umumnya, agar akun kamu tetap aman, kamu hanya akan diizinkan untuk log in via aplikasi Authenticator.

description: Warning that appears when we ask user for password after they turn on authenticator.
english: Warning: If you choose to enable 2-Step Verification via both Email and the Authenticator App, you will be forced to use the Authenticator App for verification in most cases.
translation: Peringatan: Jika kamu mengaktifkan Verifikasi Dua Langkah via email dan aplikasi Authenticator, umumnya, kamu akan diharuskan untuk menggunakan aplikasi Authenticator untuk verifikasi.

english: Please input a whole number between 0 and {maxSpendLimit}

This setting controls notifications on spend sent to the verified parental email on the under {age} user's account. Parents who select the default will only receive email notifications when spend levels are exceedingly high in a given calendar month.
translation: Pengaturan ini mengendalikan notifikasi yang dikirim ke email orang tua tentang pengeluaran untuk akun dengan pengguna yang berusia di bawah {age} tahun. Orang tua yang memilih default hanya akan menerima notifkasi email jika level penggunaan sangat tinggi dalam suatu bulan.

description: Parental spend control launch email, Korean user over 70000 KRW limit
english: {paragraphStart}This email is to inform you that the monthly spend restrictions for account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} of {emphasisStart}{amountUsd} USD{emphasisEnd} per month has been changed in accordance with local regulator requirements. These regulations require that accounts held by users under the age of 18 do not spend more than 70,000 KRW per month. As a result, your monthly spend restriction has been updated to {emphasisStart}70,000 KRW{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}You can make changes to your monthly spend restriction settings in {parentalControlsLinkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} at any time, but you will not be able to remove this restriction or set a limit above 70,000 KRW. For more information on Parental Controls, please visit the {helpCenterLinkStart}Help Center{linkEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Email ini untuk menginformasikan kamu bahwa batasan pengeluaran bulanan untuk akun {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} dengan {emphasisStart}{amountUsd} USD{emphasisEnd} per bulan telah diubah sesuai dengan persyaratan peraturan lokal. Peraturan ini mensyaratkan bahwa akun dengan pengguna yang berusia di bawah 18 tahun tidak dapat memakai lebih dari 70.000 KRW per bulan. Oleh karena itu, batasan pengeluaran bulanan kamu telah di-update menjadi {emphasisStart}70.000 KRW{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}Kamu dapat mengubah pengaturan pengeluaran bulanan di {parentalControlsLinkStart}Kendali Orang Tua{linkEnd} kapan saja, tetapi kamu tidak akan dapat menghapus pembatasan ini atau mengatur batas menjadi lebih dari 70.000 KRW. Untuk informasi selengkapnya tentang Kendali Orang Tua, kunjungi {helpCenterLinkStart}Pusat Bantuan{linkEnd}. {paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Terima kasih,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}Tim Roblox{emphasisEnd}

description: Parental spend control launch email, for Korean user with limit under 70000 KRW
english: {paragraphStart}This email is to inform you that we now support setting monthly spend restrictions in your local currency, KRW. As a result, the spend restrictions for account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} of {emphasisStart}{amountUsd} USD{emphasisEnd} per month has been updated to {emphasisStart}{amountLocalCurrency} KRW{emphasisEnd} per month.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}In addition, local regulators require that accounts held by users under the age of 18 do not spend more than 70,000 KRW per month. You can make changes to your monthly spend restriction settings in {parentalControlsLinkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} at any time, but you will not be able to remove this restriction or set a limit above 70,000 KRW.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}For more information on Parental Controls, please visit the {helpCenterLinkStart}Help Center{linkEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Email ini untuk menginformasikan kamu bahwa sekarang batasan pengeluaran bulanan tersedia dalam mata uang lokal kamu, KRW. Oleh karena itu, batasan pengeluaran untuk akun {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} dengan {emphasisStart}{amountUsd} USD{emphasisEnd} per bulan telah di-update menjadi {emphasisStart}{amountLocalCurrency} KRW{emphasisEnd} per bulan.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}Selain itu, peraturan lokal mensyaratkan bahwa akun dengan pengguna yang berusia di bawah 18 tahun tidak dapat memakai lebih dari 70.000 KRW per bulan. Kamu dapat mengubah pengaturan pengeluaran bulanan di {parentalControlsLinkStart}Kendali Orang Tua{linkEnd} kapan saja, tetapi kamu tidak akan dapat menghapus pembatasan ini atau mengatur batas menjadi lebih dari 70.000 KRW.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}Untuk informasi selengkapnya tentang Kendali Orang Tua, kunjungi{helpCenterLinkStart}Pusat Bantuan{linkEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Terima kasih,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}Tim Roblox{emphasisEnd}

description: Parental spend controls launch email, for non-korean users whose local currency is supported and enabled
english: {paragraphStart}This email is to inform you that we now support setting monthly spend restrictions in your local currency, {emphasisStart}{currencyCode}{emphasisEnd}. As a result, the spend restrictions for account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} of {emphasisStart}{amountUsd} USD{emphasisEnd} per month has been updated to {emphasisStart}{amountLocalCurrency} {currencyCode}{emphasisEnd} per month.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}You can make changes to your monthly spend restrictions in your local currency or disable this setting entirely in {parentalControlsLinkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} at any time. For more information on Parental Controls, please visit the {helpCenterLinkStart}Help Center{linkEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Email ini untuk menginformasikan kamu bahwa sekarang batasan pengeluaran bulanan tersedia dalam mata uang lokal kamu, {emphasisStart}{currencyCode}{emphasisEnd}. Oleh karena itu, batasan pengeluaran untuk akun {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} dengan {emphasisStart}{amountUsd} USD{emphasisEnd} per bulan telah di-update menjadi {emphasisStart}{amountLocalCurrency} {currencyCode}{emphasisEnd} per bulan.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}. Kamu dapat mengubah pengaturan pengeluaran bulanan dalam mata uang lokal kamu atau menonaktifkan pengaturan ini di {parentalControlsLinkStart}Kendali Orang Tua{linkEnd} kapan saja. Untuk informasi selengkapnya tentang Kendali Orang Tua, kunjungi{helpCenterLinkStart}Pusat Bantuan{linkEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Terima kasih,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}Tim Roblox{emphasisEnd}

english: Changes to your Monthly Spend Restrictions settings
translation: Perubahan atas pengaturan Batasan Pemakaian Uang Bulanan

english: Your Monthly Spend Restrictions settings have been changed
translation: Pembatasan Pemakaian Uang Bulanan kamu telah diubah

english: Your Monthly Spend Restrictions settings have been reset
translation: Batasan Pemakaian Uang Bulanan kamu telah direset

english: {paragraphStart}This email is to inform you that the country and purchase currency associated with the account {username} has recently changed. As a result, your previously set spend restrictions of {amount} {previousCurrency} per month have been reset and no longer apply to future purchases on this account. To set a new monthly spend restriction for the account in {newCurrency}, please visit {parentalControlsLinkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} in Settings.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}The Roblox Team
translation: {paragraphStart}Email ini untuk menginformasikan kamu bahwa negara dan mata uang pembelian yang terhubung dengan akun {username} telah diubah baru-baru ini. Oleh karena itu, batasan pengeluaran sebelumnya, yaitu {amount} {previousCurrency} per bulan, telah direset dan tidak lagi berlaku untuk pembelian berikutnya di akun ini. Untuk mengatur batasan pengeluaran dalam {newCurrency}, kunjungi {parentalControlsLinkStart}Kendali Orang Tua{linkEnd} di pengaturan.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Terima kasih,{lineBreak}Tim Roblox

english: How do I use voice chat?

You can use voice chat in any experience where the developer has enabled it. Voice audio and game sounds will automatically play through your speaker or headphones as you join an experience. You’ll be able to speak with other users through your microphone.
translation: Kamu dapat menggunakan chat suara di pengalaman virtual mana pun dengan chat suara yang telah diaktifkan oleh developer. Suara pengguna dan game akan diputar secara otomatis melalui speaker atau headphone saat kamu bergabung ke pengalaman virtual. Kamu akan dapat berbicara dengan pengguna lain melalui mikrofon kamu.

english: How can I stay safe while using voice chat?
translation: Bagaimana saya dapat tetap dalam keadaan aman saat menggunakan chat suara?

english: This setting allows qualified users to use voice to communicate in Roblox experiences. You are expected to follow the {startLink}Roblox Community Standards{endLink} while using this feature. If you see others breaking the rules, please report abuse to let us know.
translation: Pengaturan ini mengizinkan pengguna yang memenuhi syarat untuk menggunakan suara dalam berkomunikasi di pengalaman virtual Roblox. Kamu diharapkan untuk mengikuti {startLink}Standar Komunitas Roblox{endLink} saat menggunakan fitur ini. Jika kamu melihat pengguna lain melanggar aturan, laporkan penyalahgunaan tersebut kepada kami.

description: Previously Description.VoiceChatInfo.SafePreBody + Description.VoiceChatInfo.FAQ + .
english: If you hear someone using harmful or dangerous language, please mute them and file an abuse report. For moderation and safety purposes, Roblox may record voice audio anywhere on the platform. More information in our {startLink}Voice Recording FAQ{endLink}.
translation: Jika kamu mendengar pengguna lain menggunakan kata yang membahayakan, bisukan mereka dan kirim laporan penyalahgunaan. Untuk keperlukan moderasi dan tujuan keamanan, Roblox dapat merekam audio suara di mana pun di platform. Untuk informasi selengkapnya, kunjungi {startLink}Pertanyaan Umum Rekaman Suara{endLink}.

english: Success! Monthly Spend Restrictions have been set up.
translation: Pembatasan Pemakaian Uang Bulanan sudah berhasil diatur.

english: I consent to Roblox’s collection, use, and storage of my voice recording for moderation and safety purposes only.
translation: Saya setuju akan pengumpulan, penggunaan, dan penyimpanan rekaman suara saya hanya untuk keperluan moderasi dan tujuan keamanan.

english: This phone number is not valid. Please enter a different phone number.
translation: Nomor telepon ini tidak valid. Masukkan nomor telepon yang berbeda.

english: This phone number cannot be used. Please enter a different phone number.
translation: Nomor telepon ini tidak dapat digunakan. Masukkan nomor telepon yang berbeda.

english: Roblox uses your contacts to help you and your contacts find each other on Roblox. {linkStart}Learn more{linkEnd}{lineBreak}You must have a verified phone number to use this feature.
translation: Roblox menggunakan kontakmu untuk membantu kamu dan kontakmu menemukan satu sama lain di Roblox. {linkStart}Pelajari Selengkapnya.{linkEnd}{lineBreak}Kamu harus memiliki nomor ponsel terverifikasi untuk menggunakan fitur ini.

english: Do you want to be recommended to Roblox users who have your phone number?
translation: Akun kamu ingin direkomendasikan ke pengguna Roblox yang memiliki nomor ponsel kamu?

english: When using Roblox, users with your phone number will be able to see your name as saved in their device.
translation: Saat menggunakan Roblox, pengguna yang memiliki nomor ponsel kamu akan dapat melihat nama kamu yang tersimpan di perangkat mereka.

english: Allow Access To This Device’s Contacts
translation: Izinkan Akses ke Kontak Perangkat Ini

english: Roblox will periodically sync your device contacts to give you the most up to date recommendations. Only matches with existing Roblox users will be stored on Roblox servers.
translation: Roblox akan menyinkronkan kontak perangkat kamu secara berkala untuk memberikan rekomendasi terbaru. Hanya kecocokan dengan pengguna Roblox yang sudah ada yang akan disimpan di server Roblox.

english: When you remove access to your device contacts, you’ll have the option to delete your synced contact data.
translation: Saat kamu menghapus akses ke kontak perangkatmu, kamu akan memiliki opsi untuk menghapus data kontak yang tersinkron.

english: Your phone number is not verified.

This will delete your contact data that was synced from this device only. If you’ve synced contact data on multiple devices, you must do this separately per device. To delete all synced data from every connected device at once, go to your privacy settings on a desktop web browser.
translation: Ini akan menghapus data kontak yang disinkronkan hanya dari perangkat ini. Jika kamu telah menyinkronkan data kontak di beberapa perangkat, kamu harus menghapusnya di setiap perangkat. Untuk menghapus secara sekaligus semua data tersinkron dari semua perangkat yang terhubung, buka pengaturan privasi di browser desktop.

english: Unable to delete synced contact data.
translation: Tidak dapat menghapus data kontak tersinkron.

english: You have not verified your phone number.
translation: Kamu belum memverifikasi nomor ponsel kamu.

english: When this setting is enabled, this account can only access content that is appropriate for all audiences. Additionally, Communication Settings will be set to Off.
translation: Saat pengaturan ini diaktifkan, akun ini hanya dapat mengakses konten yang sesuai untuk semua pengguna. Selain itu, Pengaturan Komunikasi akan dimatikan.

english: Communication Settings are locked because Account Restrictions are enabled
translation: Pengaturan Komunikasi terkunci karena Batasan Akun diaktifkan

english: Successfully updated access to this device's contacts.
translation: Berhasil meng-update akses ke kontak perangkat ini.

english: Failed to update access to this devices contacts.
translation: Gagal meng-update akses ke kontak perangkat ini.

english: To enable contacts, go to Add Friends in the Roblox app on your mobile device.
translation: Untuk mengaktifkan kontak, buka Tambahkan Teman di aplikasi Roblox di perangkat seluler.

description: Tab menu value for OAuth Authorizations
Sub-header message describing what items are in the below app permissions table view
english: Change the permissions of external apps that have access to your information.
translation: Ubah izin aplikasi eksternal yang memiliki akses ke informasi kamu.

english: Enable voice chat to talk with others in this experience.
translation: Aktifkan chat suara untuk berbicara dengan pengguna lain di pengalaman virtual ini.

english: Follow our {linkStart}Community Standards{linkEnd} when talking and report abuse if you hear it.
translation: Ikuti {linkStart}Standar Komunitas{linkEnd} kami saat berbicara dan laporkan penyalahgunaan jika kamu mengetahuinya.

english: I consent to Roblox’s collection, use, and storage of my {linkStart}voice recording{linkEnd} for moderation and safety purposes only.
translation: Saya setuju akan pengumpulan, penggunaan, dan penyimpanan {linkStart}rekaman suara{linkEnd} saya oleh Roblox hanya untuk keperluan moderasi dan tujuan keamanan.

description: similar to Label.ConsentVoiceCollection
english: By clicking on enable, I consent to Roblox’s collection, use, and storage of my {linkStart}voice recording{linkEnd} for moderation and safety purposes only.
translation: Dengan mengklik aktifkan, saya setuju akan pengumpulan, penggunaan, dan penyimpanan {linkStart}rekaman suara{linkEnd} saya oleh Roblox hanya untuk keperluan moderasi dan tujuan keamanan.

description: Confirmation modal message before deleting an OAuth app authorization
english: Are you sure you want to remove the authorization for "{appName}"?
translation: Kamu yakin ingin menghapus otorisasi untuk "{appName}"?

description: Confirmation dialog modal header
Successful authorization deletion message
english: The authorization to "{appName}" was successfully removed

description: Error message if authorization deletion fails
english: There was an error removing the authorization. Please try again.
translation: Terjadi eror saat menghapus otorisasi. Coba lagi nanti.

description: Button text

english: Once you begin this process, this account will no longer be accessible and the deletion cannot be reversed.
translation: Begitu kamu memulai proses ini, akun ini tidak akan lagi dapat diakses dan penghapusan tidak dapat dibatalkan.

description: A warning to users that changing their username will remove their verified badge status
english: Warning: Changing your username will remove your verified badge status. Are you sure you want to do this?
translation: Peringatan: Mengubah nama pengguna kamu akan menghapus status lencana terverifikasi. Kamu yakin ingin melakukannya?

description: A warning to users that turning off their 2FA will remove their verified badge status
english: Warning: Turning off your 2FA will remove your verified badge status. Are you sure you want to do this?
translation: Peringatan: Mematikan Verifikasi Dua langkah akan menghapus status lencana terverifikasi. Kamu yakin ingin melakukannya?

description: Placeholder text when an OAuth app has no description.

english: Use a physical key, your device's face ID, or touch ID to validate your identity.
translation: Gunakan kunci fisik, Face ID, atau Touch ID perangkat kamu untuk memverifikasi identitas kamu.

english: Supported on web browsers, iPhone, and iPad. A hardware security key or device’s biometrics like fingerprint or facial recognition.
translation: Didukung di browser web, iPhone, dan iPad. Kunci keamanan hardware atau biometrik perangkat seperti sidik jari atau pengenalan wajah.

english: Receive unique security codes at your specified email.
translation: Terima kode keamanan unik di email yang sudah kamu tentukan.

english: Receive unique security codes by text message on your phone.
translation: Terima kode keamanan unik di SMS.

english: Download an app on your phone to generate unique security codes. Suggested apps include Google Authenticator, Microsoft Authenticator, and Twilio's Authy.
translation: Download aplikasi di ponsel kamu untuk membuat kode keamanan unik. Aplikasi yang disarankan seperti Google Authenticator, Microsoft Authenticator, dan Twilio Authy.

english: An Extra Layer of Account Security {lineBreaks}In addition to your password, add an extra layer of protection to your account with 2-Step Verification at login, account recovery, and high-value transactions. Note: you can only enable one option below at a time.
translation: Lapisan Tambahan Kemanan Akun {lineBreaks}Selain kata sandi kamu, berikan lapisan keamanan tambahan ke akun kamu dengan Verifikasi Dua Langkah saat log in, pemulihan akun, dan transaksi dengan nilai besar. Catatan: kamu hanya dapat mengaktifkan satu opsi di bawah dalam satu waktu.

english: Insert your key in your computer’s USB port and touch it when prompted.
translation: Masukkan kunci ke port USB komputer lalu sentuh saat diminta.

english: Alternatively, set up this device using fingerprint or facial recognition.
translation: Alternatif lain, atur perangkat ini menggunakan sidik jari atau pengenalan wajah.

english: Please try to set up your key again. If you’re still unable to set up, try another key.
translation: Coba atur kunci kamu lagi. Jika kamu masih tidak dapat mengaturnya, coba kunci yang lain.

english: Name your key so that later you will know which one it is.
translation: Beri nama kunci agar nanti kamu dapat mengidentifikasi setiap kunci dengan mudah.

english: Next time you sign in on web, you’ll use your security key with 2 Step Verification.
translation: Jika nanti kamu sign in di web, kamu akan menggunakan kunci keamanan dengan Verifikasi Dua Langkah.

english: {registeredKeysCount} out of {totalKeysCount} keys have been registered.
{registeredKeysCount} out of {totalKeysCount} keys have been registered. If you want to set up more keys, please delete 1 or more existing keys.
translation: {registeredKeysCount} dari total {totalKeysCount} kunci telah didaftarkan. Jika kamu ingin mengatur lebih banyak kunci, hapus satu atau lebih kunci yang sudah ada.

english: Security keys protect your robux, experiences, limiteds and more. We would recommend deleting a key if you have lost it or it is no longer valid. {lineBreak}{lineBreak}Are you sure you want to delete your key?
translation: Kunci keamanan melindung robux, pengalaman virtual, item terbatas, dan lainnya. Kami sarankan untuk menghapus kunci kalau kunci tersebut hilang atau tidak valid lagi. {lineBreak}{lineBreak}Kamu yakin ingin menghapus kunci?

english: Choose the {linkStart}highest age guideline{linkEnd} of experiences this account can join.

By saving, you agree to Stripe’s {stripeTermsOfUseLinkStart}Terms of Use{stripeTermsOfUseLinkEnd} and {stripePrivacyPolicyLinkStart}Privacy Policy{stripePrivacyPolicyLinkEnd}.
translation: Jika kamu menyimpan informasi pembayaranmu, metode tersebut akan menjadi metode pembelian default untuk semua pembelian di masa mendatang. Kamu dapat menghapus informasi pembayaran tersimpan kapan saja. Informasi pembayaran akan disimpan oleh Stripe, Inc. Dengan menyimpan metode pembayaran, kamu setuju dengan {stripeTermsOfUseLinkStart}Ketentuan Penggunaan{stripeTermsOfUseLinkEnd} dan {stripePrivacyPolicyLinkStart}Kebijakan Privasi{stripePrivacyPolicyLinkEnd} Stripe.

english: You cannot modify your payment methods on mobile. For billing and payment questions, please see the {billingHelpLinkStart}billing help pages{billingHelpLinkEnd}.
translation: Kamu tidak dapat mengubah metode pembayaranmu di ponsel. Untuk pertanyaan penagihan dan pembayaran, kunjungi {billingHelpLinkStart}halaman bantuan penagihan{billingHelpLinkEnd}.

english: Something went wrong. We could not save your card. Please try again later.
translation: Terjadi eror. Kami tidak dapat menyimpan kartu kamu. Coba lagi nanti.

english: Your Roblox Credit was successfully converted to Robux!
translation: Dana Robux kamu berhasil dikonversi ke Robux!

description: The legal consent a user agrees to by choosing to verify their age on roblox.com.
english: By clicking 'Verify My Age' you will be completing an ID verification process operated by our third party service provider. You also consent to the collection, use, and sharing of your biometric data as described in the {linkStart}Roblox Biometric Privacy Notice{linkEnd}.
translation: Dengan mengklik Verifikasi Umur Saya, kamu akan menyelesaikan proses verifikasi ID yang dijalankan oleh penyedia layanan pihak ketiga kami. Kamu juga menyetujui pengumpulan, penggunaan, dan pembagian data biometrik kamu seperti yang dijelaskan di {linkStart}Pemberitahuan Privasi Biometrik Roblox{linkEnd}.

description: First part of the body text for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is directed at the parent of the user. Below this text is an "I Agree, Validate Email" button that the parent can click to proceed.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}This email is being sent to give you notice about your child’s account on Roblox, {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}, and the option to validate your email address to enable added security and parental controls for your child’s account.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}When your child first created an account on Roblox, we collected the following information: username, password, birthdate, and gender. You or your child recently added a parent email address to the account. Please confirm that this email address is correct by {emphasisStart}clicking the button below:{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Hai,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Email ini dikirim untuk memberi tahu Anda tentang akun anak Anda di Roblox, {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}, dan opsi untuk memvalidasi alamat email Anda guna mengaktifkan keamanan tambahan dan kendali orang tua untuk akun anak Anda.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Saat anak Anda pertama kali membuat akun di Roblox, kami mengumpulkan informasi berikut: nama pengguna, kata sandi, tanggal lahir, dan jenis kelamin. Baru-baru ini Anda atau anak Anda memasukkan alamat email orang tua ke akun tersebut. Konfirmasikan bahwa alamat email ini benar dengan {emphasisStart}mengklik tombol di bawah:{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description:
Text of the button in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. The text of this button is referred to by name in the first part of the email body ('By clicking "I Agree, Validate Email"...'), so the name should be consistent with 
Description.VerificationEmail.Body.Under13.V4.
english: {paragraphStart}By validating your email address, you will have the ability to reset your child’s password (when necessary), get updates on your child’s account activities, and set your child's safety and parental control settings for their Roblox account at https://www.roblox.com/my/account#!.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}If you do not validate your email address, your child will still be able to use their account, play on Roblox and access most features, including filtered text chat.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your email address will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Apart from a parent’s email, we do not otherwise collect, use, or disclose personal information from child users.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Please review our privacy policy for more information at https://www.roblox.com/info/privacy.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Parent's Guide to Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Roblox is an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: https://www.roblox.com/info/parents{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Other Important Information{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You may refuse to allow your child’s participation on Roblox, request that we delete your child's account, and/or request that we delete your email address at any time. To take any of these actions, please contact customer service at https://www.roblox.com/support.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}By allowing your child to maintain an account on Roblox, you agree that (a) you and your child agree to the {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox Terms{aTagEnd}, including arbitration, and (b) you will supervise and be solely responsible for your child’s use of Roblox.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thank You,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}The Roblox Team{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}Dengan memvalidasi alamat email, Anda akan dapat mereset kata sandi akun anak Anda (bila perlu), menerima update tentang aktivitas akun anak Anda, dan mengatur pengaturan keamanan dan kendali orang tua untuk akun Roblox mereka di https:// www.roblox.com/my/account#!.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Jika Anda tidak memvalidasi alamat email Anda, anak Anda akan tetap dapat menggunakan akunnya, bermain di Roblox, dan mengakses sebagian besar fitur, termasuk chat teks yang difilter.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Alamat email Anda tidak akan digunakan untuk tujuan lain, diungkapkan kepada pihak ketiga, atau digabungkan dengan informasi pribadi lainnya yang dikumpulkan dari anak Anda. Selain email orang tua, kami tidak mengumpulkan, menggunakan, atau mengungkapkan informasi pribadi dari pengguna anak.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Harap review kebijakan privasi kami untuk informasi lebih lanjut di https://www.roblox.com/info/privacy.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Panduan Orang Tua tentang Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Roblox adalah platform hiburan online yang memungkinkan anak untuk berimajinasi, berkreasi, dan bermain bersama dalam dunia 3D buatan pengguna yang imersif.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Kami menyarankan Anda mengunjungi Panduan Orang Tua kami untuk membantu Anda mengenal platform kami dan menemukan tip bermanfaat untuk menciptakan pengalaman positif bagi anak Anda di Roblox: https://www.roblox.com/info/parents{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Informasi Penting Lainnya{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Anda dapat menolak partisipasi anak Anda di Roblox, meminta kami untuk menghapus akun anak Anda, dan/atau meminta kami menghapus alamat email Anda kapan saja. Untuk melakukan salah satu tindakan ini, hubungi dukungan pelanggan di https://www.roblox.com/support.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Dengan mengizinkan anak Anda memiliki akun di Roblox, Anda setuju bahwa (a) Anda dan Anda anak menyetujui {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Ketentuan Roblox{aTagEnd}, termasuk arbitrase, dan (b) Anda akan memonitor dan bertanggung jawab sepenuhnya atas penggunaan Roblox anak Anda.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Terima Kasih,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Tim Roblox{paragraphEnd}

english: This will delete previously synced contact data from all devices connected to your account. Any connected devices with access to contacts turned on will continue regularly syncing contacts with Roblox. To stop syncing contacts from a connected device, turn off access to the device contacts in Roblox privacy settings.
translation: Ini akan menghapus data kontak yang disinkronkan sebelumnya dari semua perangkat yang terhubung ke akun kamu. Setiap perangkat terhubung dengan akses ke kontak yang diaktifkan akan terus menyinkronkan kontak dengan Roblox secara berkala. Untuk berhenti menyinkronkan kontak dari perangkat yang terhubung, matikan akses ke kontak perangkat di pengaturan privasi Roblox.
